snippet.title: Minecraft x NERF World DLC
snippet.description: Wield your favorite Nerf blasters in Minecraft: Bedrock Edition! The free Nerf World DLC brings thrilling challenges, parkour levels, and arena mob battles that put your reflexes and aim to the test. Choose between in-game versions of Nerf products, including the new Ender Dragon blaster. Can you blast your way to the final boss?
